FBIS4-15012 "drsov066_b_94013" FBIS-SOV-94-066 Daily Report 5 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political Issues Yeltsin Appoints Safonov CI Deputy Director Yeltsin Appoints Safonov CI Deputy Director LD0504153494 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1449 GMT 5 Apr 94 LD0504153494 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Moscow April 5 TASS -- Russian President Boris Yeltsin signed a decree appointing Colonel-General Anatoliy Yefimovich Safonov first deputy director of the Federal Service of Counterintelligence of the Russian Federation. The same decree relieves Anatoliy Safonov from the post of the deputy director of the Federal Service of Counterintelligence. This was reported by the press service of the president of the Russian Federation.
